{"id":2169,"content":"<TABLE style=\"WIDTH: 480px; BORDER-COLLAPSE: collapse; HEIGHT: 955px\" cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 border=0>\r\n<TBODY>\r\n<TR>\r\n<TD class=3 vAlign=top align=middle width=90>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P><A href=\"#\"><IMG height=53 src=\"/yh/images/2005/04/bu4.jpg\" width=69 border=0></A></P>\r\n<P><A href=\"#\"><IMG height=125 src=\"/yh/images/2005/04/bu10.jpg\" width=69 border=0></A></P>\r\n<P><A href=\"#\"><IMG height=99 src=\"/yh/images/2005/04/Yh_04_04.jpg\" width=69 border=0></A></P>\r\n<P><A href=\"#\"><IMG height=56 src=\"/yh/images/2005/04/Yh_04_10.jpg\" width=69 border=0></A></P>\r\n<P><A href=\"#\"><IMG height=72 src=\"/yh/images/2005/04/Yh_04_15.jpg\" width=69 border=0></A><BR><BR></P></TD>\r\n<TD class=3 vAlign=top align=left>\r\n<P><STRONG>［春秋笔］</STRONG><BR><A href=\"/html/cqb/2008/416/0841612453D899113745D1756K62KB1CB4.html\" target=_blank>民办教育在民国的兴衰</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．．．李兴韵<BR><A href=\"/html/cqb/2008/416/08416125311HHIJ1375BCCFB9J4GI4HD57.html\" target=_blank>龙云与民主堡垒西南联大</A>．．．．．．．．．黎　勤　李　凌<BR><A href=\"/html/cqb/2008/416/0841612634HDAJE13763198GIICG1H6913.html\" target=_blank>北洋军阀时期为何也有“民主”</A>．．．．．．．．．．李庶民<BR><A href=\"/html/cqb/2008/416/0841612744GID1E1377BJ8F756AH352F9D.html\" target=_blank>胡适与国民党的冲突</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．张家康</P>\r\n<P><STRONG>［亲历记］</STRONG><BR><A href=\"/html/qlj/2008/416/0841612823826EE137878C7BDG83J9J694.html\" target=_blank>我随李富春访问苏联</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．阎明复<BR><A href=\"/html/qlj/2008/416/0841612927AKBD31379FA8EBDD49H830J4.html\" target=_blank>“以法治国”发稿追忆</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．．．王强华<BR><A href=\"/html/qlj/2008/416/0841612103D0KEJ138088589GG3EKA5I24.html\" target=_blank>我怎样成了小彭德怀</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．宋铭赋<BR><A href=\"/html/qlj/2008/416/084161210414C5DE13814IHEEK302E89509.html\" target=_blank>我参加的“史无前例”的学习班</A>．．．．．．．．．．万炜明</P>\r\n<P><STRONG>［求实篇］</STRONG><BR><A href=\"/html/qsp/2008/416/08416121214JI13613828829E3ABGGHFFE4.html\" target=_blank>大跃进中敢于求实的县委书记古博</A>．．．．．陈瑞华　张广桥<BR><A href=\"/html/qsp/2008/416/08416121318GJ3A813836D8J6KA72CAK93D.html\" target=_blank>《团泊洼的秋天》留传的故事</A>．．．．．．．．．．．刘仰东<BR><A href=\"/html/qsp/2008/416/0841612146B64IG138469F4CJF3HH126JB.html\" target=_blank>三年困难时期的知识分子</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．．罗平汉</P>\r\n<P><STRONG>［往事录］</STRONG><BR><A href=\"/html/wsl/2008/416/08416121448B97BA1385I777K6G01FF5DA2.html\" target=_blank>王韬与华人创办的第一份报纸</A>．．．．．．．刘小清　刘晓滇<BR><A href=\"/html/wsl/2008/416/0841612155832DGC1386D078HEG2HA93K96.html\" target=_blank>陈铭德邓季惺夫妇和《新民报》</A>．．．．．．．．．．郑连根</P>\r\n<P><STRONG>［争鸣篇］</STRONG><BR><A href=\"/html/qyt/2008/416/08416121643HI14K1387151DA4EI13I453F.html\" target=_blank>新四军军部设在皖南是党中央的战略部署吗</A>．．．．．王人广<BR><A href=\"/html/qyt/2008/416/0841612174345B651388FJD1E26J1930GC5.html\" target=_blank>《朱德追述国民党上将范石生》中部分史实核正</A>．．．赵懋家</P>\r\n<P><STRONG>［人物志］</STRONG><BR><A href=\"/html/rwz/2008/416/0841612183290B5D138944JK52848310KD6.html\" target=_blank>何思源在山东抗日</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．王秉默<BR><A href=\"/html/rwz/2008/416/08416121911DJ67H1390K417D42JH18G44D.html\" target=_blank>杨伯涛会战雪峰山</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．蒋国经<BR><A href=\"/html/rwz/2008/416/08416121949FA254139127E1B48G8296G12.html\" target=_blank>关于《陈独秀往事》的一封信</A>．．．．．．．．．．．龚育之</P>\r\n<P><STRONG>［古今谈］</STRONG><BR><A href=\"/html/gujt/2008/416/0841612203647DBI1392DB05HHH2I5I2C3B.html\" target=_blank>汉武帝与轮台罪己诏</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．王也扬<BR><A href=\"/html/gujt/2008/416/084161221213597B1393A8KI1G18AK77DEF.html\" target=_blank>历史上的平反周期率</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．吴　思<BR><A href=\"/html/gujt/2008/416/08416122155H75JH1394B4JK3991HG3E0BA.html\" target=_blank>千古奇冤陈世美</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．陈远发</P>\r\n<P><STRONG>［文配画］</STRONG><BR><A href=\"/html/qyt/2008/416/08416122231AJI0F13959G84A94501JBIAK.html\" target=_blank>玩儿圣人</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．陈四益</P></TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE>","title":"2005年第04期","time":1211551284999}